Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity

Class BlockDescription

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity.BlockDescription
public class BlockDescription extends Object
Description of a processing block within a workflow.
This class provides metadata about a processing block, including its schema, input/output characteristics, and various properties that define how it behaves within a larger workflow system.
